# Analytics-First Project Experience

This update shifts the project detail view to an **Analytics-First** approach, making campaign setup and ROI tracking the core focus.

## Navigation Enhancements

### 1. Analytics as the Primary View
The **Cấu hình Ads & ROI** tab is now the default view when opening any project. This allows you to immediately see performance data or configure tracking without navigating through multiple tabs.

### 2. Streamlined Setup for Drafts
For projects saved from AI Agents (Drafts), the Analytics tab now includes:
- **Status Banner**: A clear notice that the project is in "Draft" mode.
- **One-Click Activation**: A "Duyệt & Kích hoạt Mapping" button that promotes the project to Official and unlocks historical data entry.

## Workflow Overview

> [!IMPORTANT]
> To start seeing ROI data, you must first **Link Ads Campaigns** in the sidebar of the Analytics tab. This pulls in your actual spend from the linked marketing campaigns.

### Updated Detail Page
- **Slot 1**: Cấu hình Ads & ROI (Default)
- **Slot 2**: Thông tin dự án
- **Slot 3**: Chỉ số traffic

## Technical Improvements
- **Conditional Layouts**: `ProjectAnalytics` now handles both Official and Unofficial states gracefully with customized UI overlays.
- **Integrated Actions**: Promotion logic is now accessible directly from the Analytics dashboard, reducing friction in the "Lead to Project" conversion funnel.
